    <h>latha</h>
    <p><g>latha</g>
        <en>day</en> is a masculine <!--<a href="?xx=nouns/temporal_unit_nouns">temporal unit</a>-->
        <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common noun</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>latha</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>latha</m> – nominative/dative/genitive singular</li>
                <li><m>làithean</m> – nominative/dative/genitive plural</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="definiteness">
            <h>definiteness</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>indefinite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>latha</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>definite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>an latha</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>an latha</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>an latha</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>na làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>nan làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="number">
            <h>number</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>singular <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>latha</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>an latha</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>an latha</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>an latha</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>plural <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>na làithean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – toiseach <m>nan làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="case">
            <h>case</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>nominative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>an latha</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>na làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>dative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – ann an <m>latha</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – ann an <m>làithean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – anns <m>an latha</m></li>
